{"tid":1753670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"議會要爭取資源 勇武要打壓政權","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T09:40:36.000Z","uid":84408,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d453ac8877d53e18a830ca9d60e1d95eb9c45ad2","tid":1753670,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和勇合一 制度內外抗爭</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先恭喜各大準議員<br />\n<br />\n小小分析<br />\n當制度外未係氣候擊殺政權時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就要諗如果令制度內<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更多資源</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">令勇武抗爭嘅成本減低</span></span><br />\n同時資源更多<br />\n<br />\n我講嘅嘢好現實<br />\n單純嘅勇武抗爭會變<span style=\"color: red;\">烏克蘭</span><br />\n嚴格黎講係<span style=\"color: red;\">失敗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我絕對認同 一個國家或地區<br />\n爭取民主嘅進程一定會流血<br />\n<br />\n但流多或流小 制度絕對有好大影響<br />\n制度即係資源 資源多 勇武抗爭就會更加容易<br />\n易搖政權將會更大威力<br />\n<br />\n所以和勇必須要同步進行<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">議會要爭取資源 勇武要打壓政權</span></span>"},{"pid":"cac7234d9500dfda48d7da872de815d8347e964c","tid":1753670,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:02:44.000Z","msg":"兩者不可分割<br />\n不可暫停<br />\n時間好快 戰線要全部開啟"},{"pid":"e0fe6d17571f7d817a0a9803bf334daa2a9b5e90","tid":1753670,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:05:40.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd65205399ba8933d144c1f48de2ccdc303363ac","tid":1753670,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:06:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"03f6bebd2ab6278eac37af98825c034a96fe483b","tid":175